Cominco Ltd said it is forming a newpublicly held company, Cominco Resources International Ltd, tocontinue exploration and development of its mineral holdingsoutside Canada, Alaska and Australia.    Cominco will maintain a majority position in the company,but the remaining interest will be sold in offerings led byWood Gundy Inc and First Marathon Securities Ltd in Canada, andS.G. Warburg Securities and Wood Gundy Inc internationally.    Cominco said it is filing a preliminary prospectus withsecurities regulators in all Canadian provinces.                           Reuter&#3;